<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= mode === 'create' ? '新增班级' : '编辑班级' %> - 学生信息管理系统</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="app-page">
  <div class="app-shell">
    <%- include('partials/sidebar', {
      activePage: 'classForm',
      user: typeof user !== 'undefined' ? user : null,
      sidebarStats: typeof sidebarStats !== 'undefined' ? sidebarStats : null
    }) %>

    <div class="app-content">
  <header class="subpage-topbar">
    <div class="subpage-topbar-inner">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow mb-1">Student Hub</p>
        <h1 class="page-title mb-0"><%= mode === 'create' ? '新增班级' : '编辑班级' %></h1>
      </div>
      <a href="/classes" class="btn btn-outline-light">返回班级面板</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="subpage-main">
    <section class="form-layout">
      <article class="panel form-panel">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <div>
            <p class="section-kicker">Class Info</p>
            <h3>班级基础资料</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="<%= formAction %>" method="POST" class="row g-3">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label class="form-label" for="class_name">班级名称</label>
            <input id="class_name" type="text" name="class_name" class="form-control" value="<%= classItem.class_name || '' %>" required />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <label class="form-label" for="grade">年级</label>
            <input id="grade" type="text" name="grade" class="form-control" value="<%= classItem.grade || '' %>" required />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <label class="form-label" for="student_capacity">班级容量</label>
            <input id="student_capacity" type="number" min="1" name="student_capacity" class="form-control" value="<%= classItem.student_capacity || 40 %>" required />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label class="form-label" for="major">专业</label>
            <input id="major" type="text" name="major" class="form-control" value="<%= classItem.major || '' %>" required />
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <label class="form-label" for="counselor">辅导员</label>
            <input id="counselor" type="text" name="counselor" class="form-control" value="<%= classItem.counselor || '' %>" required />
          </div>
          <div class="col-12">
            <label class="form-label" for="monitor_name">班长</label>
            <input id="monitor_name" type="text" name="monitor_name" class="form-control" value="<%= classItem.monitor_name || '' %>" />
          </div>

          <div class="col-12 form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><%= mode === 'create' ? '保存班级信息' : '更新班级信息' %></button>
            <a href="/classes" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">取消</a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </article>

      <aside class="panel helper-panel">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <div>
            <p class="section-kicker">Guide</p>
            <h3>维护建议</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="helper-list">
          <li>班级名称尽量稳定，避免频繁改名影响历史数据检索。</li>
          <li>调整班级名称时，系统会同步更新所属学生的班级字段。</li>
          <li>删除班级前需要先处理掉班下学生，避免形成孤立数据。</li>
          <li>容量建议按实际编制维护，方便看满载率。</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
